flowchart LR
    Client[Client] -->|Command| CH[Command Handler<br/>Application Service]

    subgraph CH [Command Handler]
        direction TB
        Load[Load Aggregate<br/>replay events]
        Invoke[Call method on Aggregate]
    end

    CH --> Load
    Load --> Invoke
    Invoke --> AGG[AGGREGATE]

    subgraph AGG [AGGREGATE]
        direction TB
        Logic[Domain Logic &<br/>Invariant Validation]
        Events[Produces Domain Events]
    end

    AGG --> Logic
    Logic --> Events

    Events -->|Emits Events| ES[(Event Store)]

    ES -->|Event Stream<br/>replay / hydration| Load

    ES --> Projections[Projections]
    Projections --> RM[Read Models]

    classDef aggregate fill:#dbeafe,stroke:#1e40af,stroke-width:2px
    class AGG aggregate

    classDef handler fill:#e0e7ff,stroke:#4338ca
    class CH handler
